    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E92 M3 powered by the legendary S65B40 naturally aspirated V8, featuring individual throttle bodies and an 8,400 RPM redline. This example utilizes a traditional 6-speed longitudinal manual transmission paired with a GKN-sourced M Variable Differential Lock for superior power delivery. The chassis remains taut with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and multi-link rear geometry. Recent preventative maintenance includes rod bearing inspection and throttle actuator replacement, ensuring the high-pressure VANOS system operates flawlessly. A true driver\u2019s specification with a focus on tactile performance and linear power delivery.",
